                    </ul>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li class="light-red"><i class="fa fa-question-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i> How will I receive payment? </li>
                        <li><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right" aria-hidden="true"></i> You will receive payment through your bank account at the end of next month for jobs closed in previous months. </li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
