                            <br> * <strong>For oversea <a href="#">translators</a>, </strong> the transfer will be done once the total payment <strong>reaches 50,000 JPY</strong> (overseas remittance)
                            <br> In the case of transferring without reaching this amount, translators have to pay their own remittance fee of 2500 JPY.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
